                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 66va: Remember Bä-Ḫaylä ˀIyäsus in the time of the incense burning and the offering. His mother is ˀAlaṗis and the father of his mother is Täwäldä Mädḫən. He took a half of its price and another half he left for the church, for the sake of Ṗaraqliṭos, our God.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 217r: ያስተአረቁ፡ ፭ት፡ ሽማግሌ፡ ብላታ፡ ኀይሉና፡ ብላታ፡ ምራጭ፡ ብላታ፡ ተክለ፡ ማርያም፡ ሽቃ፡ አይሙት፡ አቶ፡ ሣህሉ።…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 217r: Those who reconciled are five elders, blatta Ḫaylu and blatta Məraḉ, blattaTäklä Maryam, šəqa ˀAymut, ˀato Śahlu…</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Erasures: e.g., fols. 12ra l. 27, 12va l. 3, l.9, 69vb l.14, 113rb l.30 (marked by two lines above), 26va ls. 14-17, 31va ls. 16-17, 51va l.21, 52va l.25, 59v l.17, 90rb ls.27-28.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasures (possible written by the same hand as that of Additiones 1 and 2): e.g., fols. 8va l.33, 12vb, l.22, 24va l.1, 59v ls.18-19, 64rb ls.4-5, 93ra ls.24-25.&#xD;
- Omitted passages or excerpts from the Gospels (?) added, possible by the same hand as that of Addiones 1,2, in the upper margins: e.g., fols. 131v-133r, 141v-142v.&#xD;
- Small numbers are added in the margins of columns on fols. 52va-54rb, &#xD;
- Drawing excercises: fols. 1v-2r.</item>
